Task #21: zero-setup trial-mode launcher

Server (license_server/server.py)
- Schema migration: is_trial / parent_config_id on licenses; is_trial /
  trial_duration_seconds / trial_max_per_subnet on build_configs;
  roblox_bundles table; partial unique index enforces one trial config
  at the DB level.
- New trial channel: TRIAL_REGISTER_SECRET, sign_response_with_secret,
  require_trial_signed_request, _trial_rate_limit_check.
- Endpoints: POST /api/trial_register, POST /api/roblox_bundle/info,
  GET /api/roblox_bundle/download/<token> (now SINGLE-USE — token is
  popped before serving), GET /download_trial public (rate-limited),
  admin /roblox_bundles upload + delete.
- Build config form takes trial duration in HOURS (converted to seconds
  server-side, min 1 hour).
- _patch_launcher_source injects IS_TRIAL + _TRIAL_REGISTER_SECRET_XOR
  into launcher.py source at build time.
- Build dashboard exposes a copyable public trial download link on each
  trial config row.

Launcher (launcher.py)
- New regex-patchable constants IS_TRIAL and _TRIAL_REGISTER_SECRET_XOR.
- _decode_trial_secret + _sign_request_with_secret /
  _verify_signature_with_secret for the separate trial HMAC channel.
- register_trial_license() POSTs to /api/trial_register; accepts both
  license_key and key in the response.
- fetch_roblox_bundle_info() + download_and_extract_roblox_bundle():
  threaded download with live splash progress, sha256 verification,
  threaded extraction with HARDENED path-traversal defense (rejects
  .., absolute, drive-prefixed entries; commonpath check),
  .bundle_version marker for skip-on-up-to-date.
- TrialExpiredDialog with "Get Full License" + "Quit" buttons (opens
  https://t.me/denfistore).
- check_license_or_prompt: in trial mode, only auto-mint when there is
  NO saved key. An existing trial key that fails validation is treated
  as expired and shows TrialExpiredDialog (no silent re-mint).
- start_license_watchdog: trial fatal expiry routes through
  TrialExpiredDialog instead of the generic LockScreen.
- do_step idx==2: in trial mode, replaces find_system_roblox/sync_files
  with bundle download+extract; first-run failures are hard-fail (no
  silent fallback to stale files).
- Non-trial path is 100% unchanged.

